      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Node Class Definition\n\nThis graph is now the canonical template for graph-native node classes.\n\n- `Port View` exposes the class artifact to host graphs\n- `Icon View` gives semantic-zoom identity\n- `Node View` carries the ordinary `node.web` implementation\n- `Editor View` carries the ordinary `editor.web` implementation\n- the default base node still renders markdown from `data.content`",
